description: In 2010 there are a high percentage of unidentified species. When sorting, there is always a pile of single leaves, small plants and stems that it is not possible to separate to identify; this can vary by year and plot
FYM applied once every four years, the last time in 2009 next in 2013 therefore none in this observation period.
Species in this data set but NOT in the 1991-2000 species dataset (http://doi.org/10.23637/rpg5-species_1991-2000-01)
